  "text": "Well then did Orion entities do this themselves? Did they hand the pen physical? Or did they do it from mental planes? Or did they use one of the incarnate entities to construct these by thought? I am Ra. Nearly all of these structures and formations were constructed at a distance by thought. A very few were created in later times in imitation of original constructs by entities upon your earth, a plane, a density.",
